{
  "stem": "18470.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it was a very exciting time for everyone because the LA school had just moved onto the campus of the University of Southern California.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We have-- we became the first Judaica division of a private university.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And HUC developed the School of Jewish Communal Service, which was the first in the country, and did new things.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was hard to leave there because I had not yet sat in my chair at USC when I had to come back to Cincinnati, the Midwest.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And after the LA experience, it was much more difficult.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Uh-huh.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My doctorate is in the field of modern Zionism.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I wrote on Ahad Ha'am, the founder of cultural Zionism.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Doctoral dissertation was called Ahad Ha'am and the World of the Bible and the Bible Tradition, and subsequently published on Ahad Ha'am's relationship to modern Jewish history and culture.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was a very formative period, because the Jerusalem school began as a school of biblical archeology.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We then added the mandatory year of study in Jerusalem in 1970 for rabbis.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I expanded that to include cantors, educators, and communal workers, and then progressively ordaining the first Israeli rabbi for Jerusalem, for Israel, the first woman rabbi for Israel.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And now, of course, we have a thriving institution there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So it's been a very busy time this last 25 years.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was designated chancellor of the college, which is a position that Dr.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Glueck would have had had he-- had he lived.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it's a senior position of spokesperson and development work.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I also want to teach, go back into the classroom.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I have some things I want to write and to begin to seriously to read again, you know.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When you're an administrator, it's very difficult to maintain Jewish scholarship.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
